# IFC VIEWER

This project is a IFC visualizer designed with Threejs and IFCjs.

The features of this project are:

-visualize ifc model - OK

-select the elements - OK

-show properties - WIP

-create spatioal tree - OK

-multithread to load the files - WIP

-edit ifc model - WIP

-see floorplans -WIP

-make annotations -WIP

-make report from IFC model - WIP

-GIS integration - WIP

# how to use it

fork this repository and clone it to your local repository.
type "npm run build" and open with live server in browser
